# Read important docs first (locked)

**Before** planning, coding, or answering "what's next" — **read these on disk** (skim only if this chat already opened them this turn):

| # | File | Why |
|---|------|-----|
| 1 | `C:\Projects\_tools\OWNER-PLAYBOOK.md` | How the owner wants replies, local-before-live, verification |
| 2 | `C:\Projects\_tools\SESSION-START.md` | Cross-project read order, rule bundle, handoff template |
| 3 | `docs/ROADMAP.md` | Current focus, phases, **New session — start here**, config locks |
| 4 | `docs/CHANGELOG.md` | What shipped recently (local vs live) |
| 5 | `AGENTS.md` | Config locks, preview command, ship workflow |
| 6 | `C:\Projects\_tools\DESIGN-FAVORITES.md` | **UI / visual work only** — owner-approved patterns to reuse |

## When to read

- **New chat** or handoff block — always, before local dev or edits
- **Theme pass, polish, visual refresh** — also read **DESIGN-FAVORITES.md**; see **`design-favorites.mdc`**
- Owner says they **like** a design → add row to **DESIGN-FAVORITES.md** same session

